All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class WebServiceWorker
extends RemoteServiceWorker

Does a call to a Web Service. This worker is started if the protocol tag in RpcInfo equals 'HTTP'. How the call is made depends on the configuration of the HTTPMethod and the MessageType.
